# Operational Resilience and Backups

- Treat baseline artifacts and truth references as first-class assets with integrity checks.
- Require checksums and lineage metadata for promoted baseline archives.
- Require periodic restore drill evidence with measured RPO and RTO.
- If restore drill fails target, block promotion-related governance updates until corrective action is documented.
- Never delete historical recovery reports; append corrections and supersession notes instead.
- Follow continuity requirements from `docs/governance/continuity-recovery.md`.
